<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.6.7">
<l>mūttavaṟ karacu vēṇṭi muṉputū teḻunta ruḷi</l>
<l>māttamar pākaṉ vīḻa matakari maruppo cittāy</l>
<l>pūttamar cōlai yōṅkip puṉalparan toḻukum nāṅkaik</l>
<l>kāttaṉē kāva ḷantaṇ pāṭiyāy kaḷaika ṇīyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who, graciously appearing long ago as a messenger</l>
<l rend="indent">requesting a kingdom for the eldest,</l>
<l>Broke the rutting elephant’s tusk so that the mahout seated on its head fell,</l>
<l>You of the cool hamlet of Kāvaḷam, preserver of Nāṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">where waters flow wide</l>
<l>With flowering, flourishing groves rising, only you are [our] refuge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
